{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/brachial-plexus-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/brachial-plexus-and-driving","title":"Brachial plexus and driving","format":"answer","details":{"need_id":"2235","business_proposition":false,"alternative_title":"","overview":"Tell DVLA if you have brachial plexus - download the correct form to let them know","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver &amp; Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> if you have brachial plexus.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>You can be fined up to £1,000 if you don’t tell <abbr title=\"Driver &amp; Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> about a medical condition that affects your driving. If you’re involved in an accident, you may be prosecuted.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Car or motorcycle licence</h2>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver &amp; Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in form G1 and send it to <abbr title=\"Driver &amp; Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_065614.pdf\" title=\"Download medical questionnaire\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘G1 - Confidential medical information’ (PDF, 283KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Bus, coach or lorry licence</h2>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver &amp; Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in form G1V and send it to <abbr title=\"Driver &amp; Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_065273.pdf\" title=\"Download medical questionnaire\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘G1V - Confidential medical information’ (PDF, 318KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n"},"updated_at":"2012-10-15T11:21:13+00:00"